00146 GrMeshIB::Cache()
00147 {
00148         unsigned int prevIB = GrGetIB();
00149         if ( !_indexBuffer )
00150         {
00151                 _dirty = 1;
00152                 _indexBuffer = GrGenIB();
00153                 GrBindIB( _indexBuffer );
00154                 bglBufferData( GL_ELEMENT_ARRAY_BUFFER, 2 * _maxIndexCount, 0, ( ( _flags & kDynamic ) != 0 ) ? GL_DYNAMIC_DRAW : GL_STATIC_DRAW );
